    - No. 4 22-100  
    - No. 200 0-10  
  - Dust Ratio: ⅔ max.  
  - Sand Equivalent 30 min.  
  - All percentages are by weight.  
  - Gravel base material retained on a No. 4 sieve shall contain not more than 0.20 percent by weight of wood waste.  

