PROMPT 98: What does ASCE 7 specify for wind pressure design on highway sign structures?
======================================================================
RESPONSE:
- Wind loads during construction must be calculated according to ASCE-7-16 (section 6.15 of Chapter 6).  
- Utilize section 29.3 of ASCE 7-16 to calculate the wind load as shown in Figure E.14.  
- W = Fh = qhGCfAf (lbs) (29.4-2, ASCE 7)  

